India’s Bonds Drop a Third Day Before RBI Policy Review

-- B y   V   R a m a k r i s h n a n
-- 
2011-09-15T03:39:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-15/india-s-bonds-drop-a-third-day-before-rbi-policy-review.html
India ’s 10-year bonds dropped a
third day before the central bank reviews its monetary policy
tomorrow. The yield on the 7.80 percent note due April 2021 rose
one basis point to 8.36 percent as of 9:06 a.m. in Mumbai,
according to the central bank’s trading system.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
